### Ascend API — Leaderboard
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Global XP leaderboard (top 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/xp?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Weekly XP leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/weekly?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Streak leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/streaks?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### My rank in the global leaderboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard/my-rank
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
